PrecisORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (1997-No.8, Fort Selkirk Historic Site, Y.T.) - which prohibits, until August 31, 2000, the staking of mineral claims or prospecting for precious minerals on some 118 hectares of land in the Yukon Territory.
